&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Maintenance Technician 1 is responsible to conduct general maintenance and repairs on facility equipment, property, and structures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duties of this job include, but are not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform assigned responsibilities, duties, and tasks according to established practices, procedures, techniques, and standards in a safe manner with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain inventory of tools, supplies, and equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean the work area, shop, and maintenance storage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform building maintenance duties (paint, electrical repairs, plumbing, carpentry, HVAC maintenance etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete a maintenance check lists and report statuses to supervisor daily&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-operate with and oversee contracted vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to emergency calls for maintenance and repairs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnose and troubleshoot issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete work orders as assigned and in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commitment &amp;amp; Dependability:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to be an integral member of a successful team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dedication to provide the highest levels of service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attendance and reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adherence to company policies and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expectation to work weekends and holidays as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Properly handle confidential customer information and other non-public company proprietary information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications &amp;amp; Education:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School diploma or equivalent preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be at least 21 years of age&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to pass a fingerprint background check to get a facility agent card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

